              <p align="justify">Prayas was initiated on 23rd march, 2009 by the students of LJIET under the guidance of Mrs. Sushma Jacob, faculty of LJIMS with the support of college management as well. Prayas mainly focuses on upbringing and educating under-privileged children. Along with the education, extra-circular activities as well as moral values are also encouraged in Prayas.</p>
             <p align="justify"> Every year the children and volunteers celebrate Prayas’s birthday by representing Prayas through the performances and cake cutting ceremony. The dignitaries, faculties, alumni as well as the director of the college are invited to be a part this celebration with us. They do appreciate the efforts by giving their time. </p>
             
              
