              <p align="justify">By hearing the word “Shopping”, not only the children but everyone gets excited and start preparing their wish-list i.e. list of the things they would like to buy. Unfortunately, there are some wish-lists which are never being fulfilled completely. So, to complete those lists every year Asmaan Foundation organises an event called “Let’s Go Shopping”. Prayas with support of Asmaan Foundation, tries to accomplish those incomplete wish-lists and give the children a real-time shopping experience.</p>
              <p align="justify">On the day of event, children are given pseudo money (fake money) through which they buy the things they like or they need. Children learn to buy, barter and bargain judiciously. Along with learning, they also enjoy shopping experience.</p>
              
              
