              <p align="justify">Independence Day is the National Festival of our country. As a citizen of India, everyone should be aware about importance this day. Every educational as well as business firm celebrates this auspicious day of independence with immense patriotism and enthusiasm. Prayas celebrates this day together with the children and volunteers including some faculties as well as the alumnis of Prayas.</p>
              <p align="justify">On this day activities like flag hoisting, acknowledging the children about history through short films, storytelling, speeches, movies, etc. are encouraged. Children do enjoy by playing small games, singing, dancing, etc. Also, a drawing competition is arranged for the children, for which they are given different prizes. </p>
              
              
