            <div class="heading-20219">
             
              <p align="justify">Sports is an important aspect for students as well as adults. Everyone is not interested in sports but as far as health is concerned everyone should do regular exercise to stay fit. Each and every school organizes sports day events for encouraging students towards sports. Also, the government supports the sports activities enthusiastically.  Hence, Prayas also motivates their children towards sports by organizing sports day once in a year.</p>
              <p align="justify">Games like relay race, kho-kho, kabbadi, trileg race, etc. are arranged on the sports day. Volunteers and children of Prayas together play some of the games. After the completion of all the games prizes are distributed amongst winners. As soon as the prize distribution is done, the children are given food packets and drinks for their fruitful efforts. Children enjoy playing different games and also maintain the discipline & follow the rules of any particular game. Hence, they learn while playing and enjoying.</p>
              
             
